不如 X<br />\n<br />\nGay cook 識玩"},{"pid":"6282d92b83347f5cd2669d20f752b5609e460749","tid":423841,"uid":118969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>a11同a10差唔係好遠啫</blockquote><br />\n多兩粒慳電core <br />\n當你效能差少  但鏡頭差別已經值得俾多個幾百<br />\n佢直接取消128 版嘅iPhone 8就係想你幫佢清舊貨<br />\n唔係邊有人買舊機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都係俾佢屈<br />\n64 唔夠用<br />\n你一係俾佢屈舊貨上7 128<br />\n一係俾佢屈食多128GB, 俾多成千...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到你想買靚鏡頭<br />\n你又會人郁想買plus<br />\nplus 得又不如 X<br />\n<br />\nGay cook 識玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鏡頭唔會8同x我就唔信有7同8咁大分別<br />\n其實每一代都係差700-800對比相同容量<br />\n所以佢每次都取消一個容量<br />\n令人錯覺買舊版抵用d<br />\n今次一年後只係平700   <br />\n但鏡頭明顯進步  我覺得抵俾<br />\n效能同mon都有提升<br />\n不過8qc真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次整雙玻璃有少少偏或者有gap我覺得正常  暫時可以接受<br />\n但機身花同某部分黃mon 鏡頭塵都係冇改善<br />\n加埋我自己個個case真係屌咗出黎"},{"pid":"3e30a474acae2b40a985d474249c2da8614141d7","tid":423841,"uid":117275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:43:11.000Z","msg":"7plus 128 認真"},{"pid":"392f054f05debdbdbefde87e43eb5bb87f2f26e4","tid":423841,"uid":16201,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"基本上我每部iphone都用2年幾3年<br />\n換機主要原因係update左ios/apps愈出愈新<br />\n搞到部機run得開始唔流暢<br />\n所以我覺得a11比a10新一代化算<br />\n起碼新一年之後就遲一年先lag<br />\n至於memory問題我本身就用開icloud <br />\n最哂位既相同whatsapp都自動上哂cloud<br />\nApps雖然多但冇玩game<br />\n所以64gb一般好夠用<br />\n2/3年之後再換部128gb已經okay"},{"pid":"082dae37725d2c7aa451c9c8c588176ff7c627f1","tid":423841,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>a11同a10差唔係好遠啫</blockquote><br />\n多兩粒慳電core <br />\n當你效能差少  但鏡頭差別已經值得俾多個幾百<br />\n佢直接取消128 版嘅iPhone 8就係想你幫佢清舊貨<br />\n唔係邊有人買舊機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都係俾佢屈<br />\n64 唔夠用<br />\n你一係俾佢屈舊貨上7 128<br />\n一係俾佢屈食多128GB, 俾多成千...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到你想買靚鏡頭<br />\n你又會人郁想買plus<br />\nplus 得又不如 X<br />\n<br />\nGay cook 識玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鏡頭唔會8同x我就唔信有7同8咁大分別<br />\n其實每一代都係差700-800對比相同容量<br />\n所以佢每次都取消一個容量<br />\n令人錯覺買舊版抵用d<br />\n今次一年後只係平700   <br />\n但鏡頭明顯進步  我覺得抵俾<br />\n效能同mon都有提升<br />\n不過8qc真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次整雙玻璃有少少偏或者有gap我覺得正常  暫時可以接受<br />\n但機身花同某部分黃mon 鏡頭塵都係冇改善<br />\n加埋我自己個個case真係屌咗出黎</blockquote><br />\n基本上X只係用oled mon、face id同前置鏡頭勁過8少少,其他野都同8一樣"},{"pid":"913734e4001b4b38106d75ce0d3a33745028311b","tid":423841,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"on9 仔先買64gb<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/194857_dce8f5c7cc63e1bae37891a8e60c8c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F194857_dce8f5c7cc63e1bae37891a8e60c8c49.jpg&h=c83bb355&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ce9832da00b86187c4f66342feef9bc9261c3bd","tid":423841,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"平果小小買過氣1年科技 <br />\n<br />\n無錢就咪換新機啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"9e18948cef1145f0cb40509cc5e68a3209072834","tid":423841,"uid":131690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T12:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9 仔先買64gb<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/194857_dce8f5c7cc63e1bae37891a8e60c8c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F194857_dce8f5c7cc63e1bae37891a8e60c8c49.jpg&h=c83bb355&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n相upload 上icloud <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690b7ebf74849c415604df33760967cf3e42dab3","