c真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次整雙玻璃有少少偏或者有gap我覺得正常  暫時可以接受<br />\n但機身花同某部分黃mon 鏡頭塵都係冇改善<br />\n加埋我自己個個case真係屌咗出黎</blockquote><br />\n7同8個鏡頭好似無乜分別咋喎</blockquote><br />\n8 low light improve左好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IN284rZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIN284rZ.jpg&h=23935eff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://images.idgesg.net/images/article/2017/09/lowlight3-100737222-large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.idgesg.net%2Fimages%2Farticle%2F2017%2F09%2Flowlight3-100737222-large.jpg&h=1415dd87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.imore.com/sites/imore.com/files/styles/larger/public/field/image/2017/09/iphone-7-plus-vs-8-plus-low-light.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imore.com%2Fsites%2Fimore.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarger%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2F2017%2F09%2Fiphone-7-plus-vs-8-plus-low-light.jpg&h=704e5b24&s={SIZE}\" /> (左7右8)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://boygeniusreport.files.wordpress.com/2017/09/dxomark-camera-scores-iphone-8-plus-iphone-8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fboygeniusreport.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F09%2Fdxomark-camera-scores-iphone-8-plus-iphone-8.jpg&h=d811a3e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de5bd9165ebc8e09838ae7ce3d905b54e8f09edf","tid":423841,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>on9 仔先買64gb<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/04/194857_dce8f5c7cc63e1bae37891a8e60c8c49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F04%2F194857_dce8f5c7cc63e1bae37891a8e60c8c49.jpg&h=c83bb355&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n相upload 上icloud <img src=\"/